data.description: Spacious home located on a Gated, all useable 2.35 acres level corner land. Home features 2,132 sqft., vaulted ceilings, skylights, 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathroom with great room in the lower level that can be a den, guest room, bonus room with 1/2 bath and a kitchenette. that can be a mother-in-law apt. Wired for generator and security alarm system. Updated Kitchen has granite counter-tops and pull-out soft close kitchen cabinets.Stainless kitchen appliances. Roof was installed about two years ago. Detached garage with 4 separate bays. Lots of room in this flat level pasture acreage with planter beds for vegetables/flowers. Room to park RV, boat, trailer & all your toy vehicles. Ideally located bordering the city limits living on acreage land.
